div.p: Implementation Detail: The PlanCandidate struct alignment ensures 0x00 to 0x3F fits within a single L1 cache line to prevent false sharing during multi-threaded plan evaluation.
Planner identifies WHERE age = 25 and retrieves nRow (1M) and cardinality (500) from sys_stats. sizeof=64 bytes (one cache line)
$Cost_{index} = (5 \times 1.0) + (500 \times 4.0)$ Random I/O penalty (4.0) applied to each row lookup. Total: 2005.0 vs Full Scan (10,000.0)
$Cost_{index} < Cost_{scan}$ Planner chooses Index Path. Compiler will emit OP_IdxGE for B-Tree traversal.
